2026-05-14T06:45:42.4641716Z 223        <!--
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4642309Z 224            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4643393Z 225            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4644204Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4645039Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4645774Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4646518Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4647336Z 230            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4648085Z 231            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-14T06:45:42.4648953Z 232            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
